Movie/Show Synopsis: A socially shunned columnist finds his romantic match online, but messaging under the wrong account causes his sleazy roommate's picture to be forwarded, creating an identity mix-up.
Movie/Show Sales Pitch: This beloved rom-com is one of the top-selling indie LGBT films of 2011, starring Nicholas Downs (NCIS: Los Angeles, The Girl Next Door) and featuring a performance by Bruce Gray (My Big Fat Greek Wedding). A heartwarming and clever film.
